ic function is advisable.', 'Synergism', 'The use of naltrexone with other potentially hepatotoxic agents should be avoided whenever possible (e.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/123176/', '', 'Oxymorphone, Tapentadol, Meperidine, Hydromorphone, Dezocine, Opium, Pentazocine, Nalbuphine, Dihydrocodeine, Naloxone, Codeine, More', 'Tamsulosin, Tinidazole, Ascorbic acid, Hydroflumethiazide, Chlorothiazide, Metronidazole, Simeprevir, Lactic acid, Mitapivat, Methazolamide, Amphotericin B, More', 1767369485);
